Fabrication ,supplying, Transportation Erection & Commissioning of second stage embedded parts of A.F.S gates Consisting of embedded parts componants such as sill beam,wheel tracks,detachable at top seal tracks. Guide rails, groovelining up to top, seal seat, seal seat bases anchorage etc. With all accessories for vertical lift fixed wheel gate including cost of materials labour, labour cess, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying one coat of zinc rich epoxy primer & three coats of cold applied coal  tar epoxy paint including cutting of required R.C.C /P.C.C for fixing of embedded parts with  civil work concreting and (also designed as per latest B.I.S code with amendment if any) all complete work as per in accordance with specifications & approved drawing & direction of E/I

Fabrication ,supplying, Transportation Erection, testing & commissioning of fixed wheel type vertical lift gate (with side and bottom seal) gate leaf consisting of skin plate, structural steel horizontal & vertical girder, bottom girder, top girder, end girder vertical stiffners, wheel,wheel pin,bearing, bearing retainers rubber seal, guide shoes, lifting brackets etc. With all accessories for  head regulator gates including all  cost of materials labour, labour cess, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying two coat chromate red oxide epoxy primer three coats of approved coal tar epoxy paint  including  required  civil work. (also designed  of gate leaf as per latest B.I.S code with amendment if any) all complete work as per in accordance with specifications & approved drawing & direction of E/I.

Fabrication ,supplying, Transportation Erection, testing & commissioning of Hoisting System of M.S Spindle Check nut system (shall be designed as par latest B.I.S code with amendments if any) etc. including cost of all materials labour, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing  applying two coats of zinc chromate red oxide primer and three coats synthetic enamel/ alluminium paint etc. as per specification & approved drawing and direction of E/I.

Fabrication ,supplying,  Erection & commissioning of structural steel & hoist bridge consisting of main beam,cross beam, chequered plate, covering hand railing, ladder with all other accessories for supporting hoisting arregement  system for operating gates including the cost of all materials  labour, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying two coats  of zinc chromate red oxide primer and three coats of approved synthetic  enamel / alluminium paint etc. as per specification & approved drawing and direction of E/I.
